TI  - A Cascade-Targeting System Delivering Polyphenol Into the Mitochondria of M1 Macrophages for Inflammatory Bowel Disease Therapy
PY  - 2026
T2  - Advanced Healthcare Materials
VL  - 15
IS  - 6
C7  - e03377
