TI  - Ameliorative effects of insoluble dietary fiber and its bound polyphenols from adzuki bean seed coat on acute murine colitis induced by DSS: The inflammatory response, intestinal barrier and gut microbiota
PY  - 2025
T2  - International Journal of Biological Macromolecules
VL  - 286
C7  - 138343
