TI  - Huanglian Wendan Decoction Improves Insomnia in Rats by Regulating BDNF/TrkB Signaling Pathway Through Gut Microbiota-Mediated SCFAs and Affecting Microglia Polarization
PY  - 2025
T2  - Molecular Neurobiology
VL  - 62
IS  - 1
SP  - 1047
