TI  - Oral food-derived whey protein isolate-Tremella fuciformis polysaccharides pickering emulsions with adhesive ability to delivery magnolol for targeted treatment of ulcerative colitis
PY  - 2024
T2  - International Journal of Biological Macromolecules
VL  - 280
C7  - 135585
DO  - 10.1016/j.ijbiomac.2024.135585
