TI  - Gastric Acid-Responsive ROS Nanogenerators for Effective Treatment of Helicobacter pylori Infection without Disrupting Homeostasis of Intestinal Flora
PY  - 2023
T2  - Advanced Science
VL  - 10
IS  - 20
C7  - 2206957
