TI  - Neutral polysaccharide from Dendrobium officinale alleviates acute alcohol-induced liver injury via the gut microbiota−short chain fatty acids−liver axis
PY  - 2025
T2  - International Journal of Biological Macromolecules
VL  - 317
C7  - 144719
