AB  - This comprehensive exploration delves into the intricate landscape of breast cancer treatment resistance, offering insights into mechanisms and innovative strategies. Advances in precision medicine, artificial intelligence, immunotherapy, splicing alterations, gut microbiota, viral onco-resistance, panomics, druggable molecular aberrations, combination therapies, natural products, and nanotechnology are spotlighted as potential solutions. Additionally, the critical need to address disparities and cultural stigmas in breast cancer care is emphasized. The narrative calls for continued collaboration, research, and integration of diverse approaches to pave the way for a future where breast cancer is effectively managed and conquered. © The Editor(s) (if applicable) and The Author(s), under exclusive license to Springer Nature Switzerland AG 2024.
